---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About ReguMe - Health Protocol Organizer" 
  description="Learn about ReguMe, the health protocol organizer for the social media age."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About ReguMe</h1>

    <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      Health Protocol Organizer for the Social Media Age
    </p>

    <div class="card">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">The Problem</h2>
      <p>
        Health advice is scattered across TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube. Influencers share 
        supplement stacks, morning routines, and wellness protocols—but keeping track of it all 
        is overwhelming. Screenshots pile up, notes get lost, and consistency becomes impossible.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">The Solution</h2>
      <p>
        ReguMe transforms social media wellness content into actionable, organized health protocols. 
        Simply paste a video URL, and our AI extracts the protocol and organizes it into:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Daily action checklists</strong> - Never forget a step</li>
        <li><strong>Supplement schedules</strong> - Track what to take and when</li>
        <li><strong>Habit reminders</strong> - Build consistency</li>
        <li><strong>Progress tracking</strong> - See what's working</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>How It Works</h2>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
      <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary); font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">1</h3>
        <h4 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">Import</h4>
        <p style="margin: 0;">Paste a video URL from TikTok, Instagram, or YouTube</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary); font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">2</h3>
        <h4 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">Extract</h4>
        <p style="margin: 0;">AI analyzes the video and extracts the health protocol</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary); font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">3</h3>
        <h4 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">Organize</h4>
        <p style="margin: 0;">Protocols are saved to your personal library</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary); font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">4</h3>
        <h4 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;">Track</h4>
        <p style="margin: 0;">Daily reminders keep you consistent</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Mission</h2>

    <div class="card" style="background: var(--accent); border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);">
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin: 0;">
        <strong>Democratize health knowledge</strong> by making wellness protocols accessible, 
        organized, and actionable for everyone.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Our Values</h2>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary); margin-top: 0;">Attribution</h3>
        <p>Always credit original creators</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary); margin-top: 0;">Safety</h3>
        <p>Strong medical disclaimers and user protection</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary); margin-top: 0;">Privacy</h3>
        <p>Your health data stays secure</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card">
        <h3 style="color: var(--primary); margin-top: 0;">Community</h3>
        <p>Share insights to help others</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Technology</h2>

    <p>Built with modern health tech stack:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>React Native</strong> - Native mobile experience</li>
      <li><strong>Supabase</strong> - Secure backend infrastructure</li>
      <li><strong>OpenAI GPT-4o</strong> - AI-powered protocol extraction</li>
      <li><strong>Social Media APIs</strong> - Content discovery</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="alert alert-warning">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">⚕️ Important Medical Disclaimer</h3>
      <p>
        ReguMe provides informational content only and is not a substitute for professional 
        medical advice. Always consult with qualified healthcare providers before following 
        any health protocols.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="/medical-disclaimer">Read our full Medical Disclaimer →</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Get Started</h2>

    <div class="card" style="text-align: center; background: var(--background);">
      <h3>Join thousands organizing their wellness journey with ReguMe</h3>
      <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        <a href="#download" class="btn">Download on the App Store</a>
      </div>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0; color: var(--text-light);">
        Questions? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> or check our <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

